name: App Icon Exporter for iOS & Android
description:
Use this file to generate all the necessary app icon/launcher assets for both iOS and Android projects.


If you find this file helpful, consider dropping me a tip (https://www.buymeacoffee.com/nathangross). If successful, I'll likely consider sharing more files.


If you have suggestions for improving this file, please consider filing out an issue on the Github page:

https://github.com/nathangross/figma-app-icon-exporter/issues
